ai-patthana15.69:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma: allows unintelligent in the Khadehaka, that is to say, the Lord of the Death,
ai-patthana15.69:1.1_0: A skillful teaching doesn’t give rise to the unsurpassable things.
ai-patthana15.69:1.1_1: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to the supreme knowledge, or an unwholesome quality.
ai-patthana15.69:1.1_3: What is not the reason for two reasons.
ai-patthana15.69:2.1_0: Unsurpassable teaching doesn’t give rise to unskillful qualities.
